Click to share on Facebook (Opens in new window)Click to share on Twitter (Opens in new window)Barbados didn’t see this one coming!
And neither did fans.
Prince Charles, 70, visited the lavish island with his wife, Camilla Parker Bowles, on Tuesday, March — and bared everything in a pair of floral swim trunks!
We don’t think we’ve ever seen the future King of England with this little amount of clothes on — and we imagine many royal fans could agree!
